{
  "stem": "9995.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they put a little electric kitchen there, although they couldn't use too much electricity because they could use only certain amount.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they were able to cook a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So it was not really that bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So long we were in ghetto, the-- the life in Cracow ghetto-- there were people who were very poor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my aunt was cooking a lot of soup and giving out to people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know that my husband's mother was having huge kettles and was-- they were financially doing OK, because believe it or not, their business before the war was just the place where was ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they still continued to have their business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they were making some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were doing not as bad as other people, and they could help others.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People were very-- actually, most of the people were helpful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What type of actions were taken in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at nighttime mainly, when the Jewish police knew that somebody was well-to-do, they were taking them to Auschwitz, and they were taking their money and whatever they had over there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, started, in 1942, the final solution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which they call it [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they really take it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all believed that they were going someplace to Ukraine, and they working over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we did not-- although they were saying that there were those supports for [GERMAN], namely places where they were killing them, we didn't believe this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't possibly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was quite some time till we realized that the people were going to their death.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Judenrat, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, very funny thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the commissar, the-- the biggest man over there, Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
